-- JPMorgan hires UBS's David Li as new China head
-- By Lawrence White
-- Wed Jul 09, 2014 10:15PM EDT
-- None



HONG KONG, July 10 (Reuters) - JPMorgan Chase & Co <JPM.N> has hired former UBS AG <UBSN.VX>  banker David Li as its new China head, the U.S. bank said on Thursday.

Li will oversee all of JPMorgan's businesses in China, reporting to Nicolas Aguzin, chairman and CEO for Asia-Pacific.